The paper discusses network intrusion detection, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). The paper also proposes a methodology for active learning, which involves machine learning techniques (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also experiments with different sampling strategies, which falls under the category of network intrusion (cs.NI) and system identification (cs.SI).
